                        <span class="user-stars allstar20 rating" title="较差"></span>
                    <span>2013-03-30</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">金刚经的白话+自身经验解读版。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="657684103">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-657684103" class="vote-count">2</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-657684103" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="657684103">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/thelongestyard/">方方土君</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2013-05-26</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">2013.3.19开始。2013.5.26结束。坦白的讲，一开始这本书看不进去也看不懂。后来遇到一些事情，碰巧又遇到人的点拨，才得以有机会静心读下去。现在我是一个唯物主义者，我并不相信宗教，但我深信所有事物背后蕴藏的逻辑与积极意义是相通的，所谓的科学与宗教并不冲突。我相信，概括来讲这本书（如果可以概括）主要是讲事物背后的三个重要特性：空性、铭印、布施，我相信，与唯物唯心无关，在空性与铭印的背后，布施更为重要，这往往也是差别的原点。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="823741208">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-823741208" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-823741208" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="823741208">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/guangyue1/">光悦Leon</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2014-07-08</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">书中第二、三部分是亮点。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="33135932">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-33135932" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-33135932" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="33135932">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/eageleye/">Jeff</a>
