  <h2>谁读这本书?</h2>
  <div class="indent" id="collector">

    

<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/57684524/"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u57684524-17.jpg" class="pil" alt="Sal" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/57684524/">Sal</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          6月25日          在读      </div>

      <br/>


    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div><br/>
    <div class="ul" style="margin-bottom:12px;"></div>
</div>
<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/121782459/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u121782459-1.jpg" class="pil" alt="刘宏来" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/121782459/">刘宏来</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          6月25日          读过      </div>

        <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
      <br/>


          <span class="">第三次读，空性的潜能，铭印影响行为，财富来于布施。静坐修铭印。面对问题，运用潜能和铭印，化危为机。</span> <br/>
    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div><br/>
    <div class="ul" style="margin-bottom:12px;"></div>
</div>
<div class="">
    
